"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal average duration: 153,703.35 µs, Anomalous average duration: 27,756,044.57 µs, Anomalous count: 29\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice->redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal average duration: 1,739.74 µs, Anomalous average duration: 7,728.95 µs, Anomalous count: 1\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error: connection error - transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout, Occurrence: 140\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error: timed out waiting for server handshake, Occurrence: 105\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 分析结果\n1. **支付服务延迟和错误**:\n   - **checkoutservice -> paymentservice** 调用的响应时间异常增长，正常时段平均响应时间为 12.83 ms，异常时段激增至 25,866.72 ms。同时，该路径也出现了大量的连接和握手超时错误。\n  \n2. **前端到结算服务的延迟**:\n   - **frontend -> checkoutservice** 调用的响应时间也在异常时段显著增长，异常再现 29 次。\n\n3. **购物车到 Redis 连接异常**:\n   - **cartservice -> redis** 的短连接延迟相对增加，尽管出现频率与延迟均不显著，但可以考虑作为次要问题进行跟进。\n\n这些征象综合表明，支付服务的连接问题是主要故障原因，它影响了从前端到结算服务的调用性能。"}
